The '''Museum of Fine Art''' was an art [[Museum/Legends|museum]] based in [[Coronet City/Legends|Coronet City]], [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. By the time of the [[Cold War (Galactic Republic–Sith Empire)|Cold War]], a diamond formed from the compressed ashes of celebrated author [[Custo Ramak]] was on display in the museum. Thousands of years later, [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn's]] mother regularly volunteered for it and in a private showing one [[New Year's Day]] her husband, [[Hal Horn|Hal]], and son were brought in as extra security.

